column5: Will be heading up to Canada this coming Saturday. Unfortunatly, will not be able to make the border until about 10-11 AM. What is the crossing time like this time of year? Any info will be appreciated.
Crossed the board about 9:30 am July 20. Had to wait for 1 car, answer the same routine questions and on my way with less than 10 min. delay. Will be going again on Aug 17Good luck.
